CustomField.description: The API name, including namespace, of the field on the Resource Request object to use as the bill rate. If blank, the value in the Suggested Bill Rate Number field is used. If that field is also blank, the value in the Requested Bill Rate field is used.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The API name, including namespace, of the field on the Resource Request object to use as the bill rate. If blank, the value in the Suggested Bill Rate Number field is used. If that field is also blank, the value in the Requested Bill Rate field is used.
CustomField.label: Resource Request Bill Rate Field
